sequenceDiagram
    participant P as 🧠 Planning Agent
    participant S as 📡 Scanner Agent
    participant F as 🔭 Frontier Agent
    participant SP as 🤖 Specialist Agent
    participant D as 🧮 Neural Net Agent
    participant E as ⚖️ Ensemble Agent
    participant M as 📲 Messaging Agent
    participant C as 🗄️ ChromaDB
    participant MO as ☁️ Modal GPU
    participant PO as 🔔 Pushover

    P->>S: Trigger RSS scan
    S-->>P: List of Deal objects

    loop For each Deal
        P->>F: Estimate price (RAG)
        F->>C: Query top-5 similar products
        C-->>F: Embeddings + metadata
        F-->>P: frontier_price: float

        P->>SP: Estimate price (fine-tuned)
        SP->>MO: Llama-3.2-3B inference
        MO-->>SP: price estimate
        SP-->>P: specialist_price: float

        P->>D: Estimate price (DNN)
        D-->>P: dnn_price: float

        P->>E: Combine estimates
        E-->>P: EnsembleResult (discount_pct, is_great_deal)

        alt is_great_deal == True
            P->>M: Send notification
            M->>PO: POST /messages.json
            PO-->>M: 200 OK
            M-->>P: notification_sent: True
        end
    end

    P->>P: Save results to memory.json
